class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔過３５＋佢地就唔做架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以無３５＋等如無左公民黨最強後盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場議會之爭一定要打落去呀　一定要爭取３５＋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係香港就玩撚猿<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51kJxZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51kJxZK.png&h=c68bfbe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">守住關鍵一席<br />\n雖然係炒冷飯，不過到２０２０香港一樣適用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔試過又點會唔知無用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人３５＋最強後盾靠你地啦</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff3b952a861142d93090ddc5e68e23422efd440","tid":2107354,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:01:41.000Z","msg":"３５＋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c6cf4aeb72aae2e5f867a7e3c7bedc615abe52","tid":2107354,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:10:50.000Z","msg":"今日割一城<br />\n明日割十城<br />\n然後得一夕安寢<br />\n<br />\n今日叫光復香港時代革命犯法<br />\n聽日35+ 否決議案就係犯法<br />\n不過35+依然係最強後盾<br />\n老虎蟹都爭取35+先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/